Searching.description:
Avicii was one of my biggest inspirations when I first began learning music production. I’ve played multiple shows with him over the years, and truly admire the space he created in electronic music. It was sad to see him go on a hiatus but upon his return to the music scene with ‘Without You’, I knew I had to put my own spin on it.

EDIT: I miss you man.

Premiered by ThisSongSlaps: http://www.thissongslaps.com/2017/10/fareoh-takes-on-avicii-and-david-guetta-in-two-incredible-remixes/
